fields.title: Something I enjoy is caring and attending to others' needs
I am always willing to put in the hard work to be helpful to others
When working with others, I often find myself arguing over small things
I am open to all types of people and accept them as they are
I don't put myself in the spotlight even if I have done something others would deem worthy
I take pride in my actions and believe that I am always right
I usually go the way others want me to even if my opinions differ
I try to prove my opinion even after others have disagreed
I always have something good to say for everyone
I often find myself criticizing other people
I always stay true to my words
I often refrain from telling the truth
I feel obligated to achieve great things
I am willing to put in the work and take all the risks that are needed for success
I always take action to prepare and plan for the future
I analyze things from every perspective
I tend to get all my work done immediately
I frequently put off my work until later
It is hard for me to focus if my workspace is not clean
I prefer not to make many plans as I end up changing them frequently
I don't stop until a task is done
It is hard for me to work consistently for long periods of time
I hold myself to very high standards and feel I can reach them
I believe that I can accomplish even the largest of my aspirations
I enjoy seeing my schedule full and keeping myself occupied
I don't feel comfortable with many responsibilities
I tend to allow others to make the decisions
I tell others my opinions, even if it is hard for them to hear
I keep the party alive
I frequently bring smiles to people's faces
I frequently take risks and believe in "Go big, or go home"
I tend to take the safest route possible without putting much on the line
People often tell me that I am a friendly person
I rarely have a hard time making new friends.
I work better with others rather than alone
I often feel that there is no need for social groups in my life
I rarely find myself having strong emotions
It doesn't take much to put me into a bad mood
I often worry about the future
I feel anxious regarding what could go wrong in a situation
I always see the positive in every situation
I complain when things don't go the way I want them to go
I often dwell on the things others say to me
It is important to me how others perceive me
I am able to control myself even if everyone is pressuring me
I am always able to maintain control over what I say
I understand the value of everything I have and I don't take things for granted
I often realize the value of things I had after I lose them
I feel most comfortable doing the things I have always done.
I try to make many changes in my life to avoid boredom
I believe in the importance of art and expression through crafts and music
I enjoy viewing art or listening to music
I have a firm understanding of my strengths and weaknesses
I am able to comprehend why I feel a certain way in different situations
I find that my mind is full of imaginative ideas
I don't have interest in abstract/fantastical ideas
I love to try new things
I tend to not take part or interest in philosophical ideas
I follow what a person of authority tells me to do, even if I may not always agree
I like to do everything my own way

Having grand ambitions never hurts; even if you don’t accomplish all of them, you’ll be a lot further down the road than if you were to think small from the start.
